title: MBMBaM 620: Face 2 Face: Djinnergy
description:
We’re on the road, so we’ve got a different show from a different road to share. Straight from the better Kansas City, we bring you the world’s first Gurt Alert. We sure were hurtin’ for a gurtin’ on this show.

Suggested Talking Points: Fast Cream for Business, The Art of Walking Down Stairs, Mr. Died in Fire, My Brother’s Idiot Fish, FILFs

Trans Youth Equality Foundation: https://www.transyouthequality.org/
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Travis McElroy, Justin McElroy, Griffin McElroy)
